author: ericvas
msg: This checkin fixes bugs in the Saver where attributes with namespaces could
be saved without a prefix, assuming the default namespace applies.  I also
removed some debug code.  Also fixed is the maintenance of the prefix map
during save so that when namespaces go out of scop, they are removed from
the prefix map, instead of being mapped to null.
